{"tid":1187084,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"有冇人有聽ragtime?","createTime":"2019-06-05T11:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T10:51:14.000Z","uid":210336,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5e6b8d31943aa9dc4a8213cb6a6fb7518e23c5f7","tid":1187084,"uid":210336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:30:33.000Z","msg":"遇著部走音舊鋼琴，點算？Ragtime就係部琴發光發熱嘅契機啦：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sE86FR2SzBo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsE86FR2SzBo&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklEltB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=348130d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sE86FR2SzBo</a><br />\nMaple Leaf Rag - Scott Joplin<br />\n<br />\nScott Joplin嘅The Entertainer同Maple Leaf Rag（上面）固然係經典，但係佢仲有<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BP69-iS4GzU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBP69-iS4GzU&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklEltB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=c7245096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BP69-iS4GzU</a><br />\nBethena - Scott Joplin<br />\n等等大量好聽嘅作品。同期仲有<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kffg-uIopO4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dkffg-uIopO4&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklEltB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=a5d4335c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kffg-uIopO4</a><br />\nBlack and White Rag - George Botsford<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tnFWgQT0bZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtnFWgQT0bZQ&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklEltB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=e48794df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tnFWgQT0bZQ</a><br />\nTwelfth Street Rag - Euday L. Bowman<br />\n<br />\n你或者會問，呢啲音樂有咩咁厲害？Well，Ragtime開創大量使用切分音嘅先河，係20世紀初美國音樂嘅代表，之後先有藍調同爵士樂嘅興起：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_94hrye_vW4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_94hrye_vW4&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklEltB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=d655e34f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_94hrye_vW4</a><br />\nThe St. Louis Blues - W.C. Handy 係咪隱約有啲ragtime味呢？<br />\n<br />\nBetween，1910年代之後唔係冇晒Ragtime嘅，例如下面呢隻2000年嘅作品雖然聽落同Maple Leaf Rag差好遠，都係Ragtime嚟：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4nofcs77hkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4nofcs77hkw&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklEltB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=641bfe01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4nofcs77hkw</a><br />\nGraceful Ghost Rag - William Bolcom<br />\n<br />\n所以想問下各位巴絲，有無聽開？有邊啲特別喜歡嘅作品？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不妨分享吓"},{"pid":"f4238d8c7d3d5227f9e43d0c5a9e8b6a3f4582b1","tid":1187084,"uid":210336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"以上係正文，下面係騎劫暨宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54061c4bdc45988438ac43aabc819767c49cbfb","tid":1187084,"uid":210336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T02:22:31.000Z","msg":"又沉"},{"pid":"a1bb39c3954089996ca86244b0135c2f7cd18714","tid":1187084,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:51:14.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好中意ragtime<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}